===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|sunne}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|sunne}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*sunnǭ}} (compare {{cog|stq|Sunne}}, West Frisian {{m|fy|sinne}}, Low German {{m|nds|Sünn}}, Dutch {{m|nl|zon}}, German {{m|de|Sonne}}, Icelandic {{m|is|sunna}}), from [[heteroclitic]] [[inanimate]] {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*sh̥₂uén}} 'sun' (compare Welsh {{m|cy|huan}}, Avestan genitive {{m|ae|𐬓𐬇𐬧𐬔}}), oblique of {{m|ine-pro|*sóh₂wl̥}}. More at {{m|en|solar}}.

